</taxonomicName>
J.-P. Castillon, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="C0A0477B6764D02EFCF4F864FC153CD8" box="[837,906,2007,2025]" pageId="6" pageNumber="167" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, échantillon 
<emphasis id="DB93FA006764D02EFC5EF864FBC73CD8" box="[1007,1112,2007,2025]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="167">Decary 9432</emphasis>
